title: Spinach mushroom quiche
ingredients: ['1 prepared 23cm pastry case', '4 eggs', '180ml milk', '1 tablespoon chopped fresh parsley', '1 teaspoon minced garlic', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '1/2 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper', '1/8 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '140g fresh spinach leaves', '225g sliced fresh mushrooms', '1/2 onion, sliced', '60g feta cheese, crumbled', '60g Swiss cheese, grated, divided']
